### ========== CUSTOMERS ==========
### CUSTOMERS - List All
GET {{url_base}}/v1/stores/{{store_id}}/customers
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### ========== PAYMENTS ==========
### PAYMENTS - List All
GET {{url_base}}/v1/stores/{{store_id}}/payments
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### ========== PRODUCTS ==========
### PRODUCTS - By SKU (Armação Ray-Ban)
GET {{url_base}}/v1/stores/{{store_id}}/products/36717
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### PRODUCTS - List All
GET {{url_base}}/v1/stores/{{store_id}}/products
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### PRODUCTS - Simplified
GET {{url_base}}/v1/stores/{{store_id}}/products/simplified
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### ========== SALES ==========
### SALES - History (Basic)
GET {{url_base}}/v1/stores/{{store_id}}/sales
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### SALES - History (With Items)
GET {{url_base}}/v1/stores/{{store_id}}/sales?withItems=true
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### SALES - Invoice History (Sale #90841)
GET {{url_base}}/v1/stores/{{store_id}}/sales/90841/invoice-history
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### SALES - Items
GET {{url_base}}/v1/stores/{{store_id}}/sales/items
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### SALES - Report
GET {{url_base}}/v1/stores/{{store_id}}/sales/report
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### SALES - Types
GET {{url_base}}/v1/stores/{{store_id}}/types-of-sales
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### ========== STOCK ==========
### STOCK - By SKU (Armação Ray-Ban)
GET {{url_base}}/v1/stores/{{store_id}}/all-stocks/36717
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### ========== STORE ==========
### STORE - Cash Flow (Custom Date)
GET {{url_base}}/v1/stores/{{store_id}}/cash-flow?receiptDate=2025-06-20
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### STORE - Cash Flow (Today)
GET {{url_base}}/v1/stores/{{store_id}}/cash-flow?receiptDate=2025-06-29
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### STORE - Info
GET {{url_base}}/v1/stores/{{store_id}}
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### ========== USERS ==========
### USERS - List All
GET {{url_base}}/v1/stores/{{store_id}}/users
Authorization: {{auth_token}}